			<name>Blindness  (1/Day)</name>
			<text>The target takes 5 (1d10) radiant damage. In addition, the target and all other creatures within 20 feet of it must each make a successful DC 17 Dexterity saving throw or be blinded until the end of the orthon’s next turn.</text>
		</action>
		<action>
			<name>Concussion</name>
			<text>The target and each creature within 20 feet of it must make a DC 17 Constitution saving throw, taking 13 (2d12) thunder damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</text>
