		</legendary>
		<legendary>
			<name>Star Spawn Larva Mage</name>
			<text>A larva mage is a nightmarish combination of a mortal body and otherworldly substance. When a powerful cultist of a wormlike entity such as Kyuss or Kezef — usually a warlock or other spellcaster — contacts the comet-borne emissary of an Elder Evil, the emissary can merge with a mortal consciousness to create a larva mage. None of the original cultist’s personality survives the transformation, so what emerges is wholly alien.</text>
		</legendary>
